How to create the perfect Schedule, with this conditions?
Padel Americano
2vs2
Total number of players: 5-12 players.
Number of courts: 2 courts available
Number of rounds: 4-16
Partnerships: No player may play with any other player more than once.
Rest: No player may rest two rounds in a row.
Game points: Each match is played to 24 points
Every player should play same amount of matches or as close as possible
Points are collected individually.
